<Verbatim PAsource="" >welcomed </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >the fine.</Rewrite>


<Verbatim PAsource="" >Richard Branson, Virgin's </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >chairman, </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >said the ruling </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >sounded </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >'the death knell' for BA's anti-competitive sales incentive arrangements and </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >would </New>
